column23: 155   public int compare(byte[] b1, int s1, int l1, byte[] b2, int s2, int l2) {156     try {157       buffer.reset(b1, s1, l1);                   // parse key1158       key1.readFields(buffer);159 160       buffer.reset(b2, s2, l2);                   // parse key2161       key2.readFields(buffer);162 163       buffer.reset(null, 0, 0);                   // clean up reference164     } catch (IOException e) {165       throw new RuntimeException(e);166     }167 168     return compare(key1, key2);                   // compare them169   }
